#RStats - experimenting with `renv`. Basically 
1 In a project, renv will look for libraries called & take a snapshot
2 Create a list of libraries+versions that can be shared (renv.lock) & do a copy to local. 
3 Anyone running the project, get the same version of them.
Awesome🧑‍🔧
